1
00:00:16,280 --> 00:00:17,679
The inherent shackles in people's hearts

2
00:00:17,879 --> 00:00:19,719
can't be broken by just one illness.

3
00:00:23,600 --> 00:00:24,559
Then I will report to the authorities.

4
00:00:24,920 --> 00:00:26,039
Even if the world hates me,

5
00:00:26,120 --> 00:00:27,600
I cannot turn a blind eye to their lives.

6
00:00:27,839 --> 00:00:28,640
I don't believe

7
00:00:28,920 --> 00:00:31,760
the authorities would ignore the lives of everyone in Chang'an.

8
00:00:35,439 --> 00:00:36,280
What should we do now?

9
00:00:36,840 --> 00:00:37,799
Since she has made her choice,

10
00:00:39,079 --> 00:00:40,119
as her close friends,

11
00:00:40,880 --> 00:00:41,920
we should support her.

12
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:44,520
Yan Ge,

13
00:00:45,039 --> 00:00:45,880
do as Xin Yue said,

14
00:00:46,280 --> 00:00:47,320
persuade other clinics

15
00:00:47,840 --> 00:00:48,640
to support us.

16
00:00:49,359 --> 00:00:51,240
I'll reach out to other influential figures

17
00:00:51,719 --> 00:00:53,280
to create public opinion.

18
00:00:54,119 --> 00:00:55,560
If the public outcry is strong enough,

19
00:00:56,439 --> 00:00:57,799
the authorities will respond.

20
00:00:58,679 --> 00:00:59,439
Mr. Si,

21
00:00:59,799 --> 00:01:01,920
you'll take over the Women's Clinic for now.

22
00:01:12,879 --> 00:01:13,439
My lord.

23
00:01:14,840 --> 00:01:15,439
Xinyue.

24
00:01:16,599 --> 00:01:17,439
Yunzhou, you're here too.

25
00:01:20,040 --> 00:01:20,560
My lord,

26
00:01:21,480 --> 00:01:22,640
the plague has been ongoing for half a month,

27
00:01:23,280 --> 00:01:24,519
and the people are in dire need of medicine.

28
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:26,480
Ren'an Hall is running low on supplies.

29
00:01:27,799 --> 00:01:29,719
I've reached out to the Imperial Court and the guild,

30
00:01:31,079 --> 00:01:33,079
and I humbly request your assistance.

31
00:01:34,079 --> 00:01:34,640
My lord,

32
00:01:35,239 --> 00:01:37,040
I'm here because the epidemic

33
00:01:37,280 --> 00:01:38,400
is spreading rapidly.

34
00:01:38,959 --> 00:01:40,239
I've identified the root cause of the disease.

35
00:01:42,959 --> 00:01:43,359
Good.

36
00:01:44,120 --> 00:01:45,120
Tell me.

37
00:01:46,280 --> 00:01:46,719
Because...

38
00:01:48,480 --> 00:01:49,200
Because the common folk

39
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:51,799
keep their loved ones' bodies at home unburied,

40
00:01:52,519 --> 00:01:53,680
and they lack knowledge of preventive measures,

41
00:01:54,200 --> 00:01:55,640
which has led to the spread of the epidemic,

42
00:01:55,719 --> 00:01:56,519
infecting countless people.

43
00:01:56,959 --> 00:01:58,159
It's customary to keep the remains

44
00:01:58,359 --> 00:02:00,000
at home and mourn the deceased,

45
00:02:00,959 --> 00:02:02,519
but now,

46
00:02:03,079 --> 00:02:03,480
the

47
00:02:04,280 --> 00:02:04,879
disease

48
00:02:05,079 --> 00:02:06,879
spreads rapidly,

49
00:02:07,519 --> 00:02:08,280
affecting

50
00:02:08,439 --> 00:02:09,319
many families.

51
00:02:09,479 --> 00:02:10,599
This practice is backfiring.

52
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:13,039
My lord, perhaps we should consult our colleagues

53
00:02:14,039 --> 00:02:14,840
and persuade the people

54
00:02:15,280 --> 00:02:16,319
to keep funerals simple

55
00:02:16,719 --> 00:02:17,520
and bury the dead promptly?

56
00:02:18,639 --> 00:02:20,240
This is no trivial matter.

57
00:02:20,759 --> 00:02:21,759
If we act rashly,

58
00:02:22,159 --> 00:02:23,360
it could stir up public discontent.

59
00:02:25,400 --> 00:02:26,560
But if we do nothing,

60
00:02:27,319 --> 00:02:28,240
the plague will spread,

61
00:02:29,039 --> 00:02:30,000
and the people of Chang'an

62
00:02:30,159 --> 00:02:31,080
will be in dire straits.

63
00:02:32,039 --> 00:02:32,759
Indeed.

64
00:02:34,039 --> 00:02:35,439
Regarding the caravan

65
00:02:35,439 --> 00:02:36,800
entering the city,

66
00:02:37,199 --> 00:02:38,879
I'll send a message to the guards.

67
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:40,680
But for the mass cremation,

68
00:02:41,199 --> 00:02:42,560
we need to report to the Emperor

69
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:44,199
for further discussion.

70
00:02:45,120 --> 00:02:45,879
This matter

71
00:02:45,879 --> 00:02:47,039
involves the rites.

72
00:02:47,520 --> 00:02:48,879
If handled improperly,

73
00:02:49,479 --> 00:02:50,919
it could lead to public discontent.

74
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:52,599
I understand.

75
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:54,280
I only ask that you

76
00:02:54,759 --> 00:02:55,800
explain the stakes to His Majesty.

77
00:02:56,280 --> 00:02:57,319
Don't let a moment of ritual

78
00:02:57,599 --> 00:02:58,879
cause a lasting regret.

79
00:03:00,520 --> 00:03:01,479
Rest assured,

80
00:03:02,159 --> 00:03:04,319
I'll enter the palace to see His Majesty

81
00:03:04,919 --> 00:03:06,319
and explain the dangers

82
00:03:07,080 --> 00:03:08,000
of the epidemic

83
00:03:08,240 --> 00:03:09,280
to him.

84
00:03:10,319 --> 00:03:11,039
Thank you, my lord.

85
00:03:13,759 --> 00:03:14,680
You seem troubled.

86
00:03:19,319 --> 00:03:21,479
Can't you even tell me?

87
00:03:26,319 --> 00:03:28,120
I just learned today that

88
00:03:28,439 --> 00:03:30,199
Lady Liu was rescued on her way

89
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:31,479
to the Supreme Court.

90
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:35,360
I'm worried she might harm you.

91
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:37,680
How about I let A'Nong

92
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:39,199
stay with you for a few days?

93
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:40,840
With the plague spreading,

94
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:43,039
you're short of hands right now.

95
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:44,960
A'Nong would just be in the way

96
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:46,159
at the clinic.

97
00:03:46,639 --> 00:03:47,280
Don't worry.

98
00:03:47,759 --> 00:03:48,800
They are all around me.

99
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:49,960
They won't leave me alone.

100
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:50,840
Trust me.

101
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:51,840
I'm telling the truth.

102
00:03:52,039 --> 00:03:52,599
Let's go.

103
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:55,240
Yan Ge, what's going on?

104
00:03:57,960 --> 00:03:59,000
I've been persuading

105
00:03:59,479 --> 00:04:00,840
other clinics according to your idea,

106
00:04:01,639 --> 00:04:03,000
hoping to unite everyone's efforts

107
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:03,759
to persuade the people.

108
00:04:04,919 --> 00:04:06,400
But they don't want to take on the trouble.

109
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:08,280
Or,

110
00:04:08,960 --> 00:04:10,280
they simply don't believe what I said.

111
00:04:15,879 --> 00:04:17,319
We've done all we can.

112
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:18,800
Don't blame yourself.

113
00:04:21,079 --> 00:04:21,920
There's still a way out.

114
00:04:22,519 --> 00:04:24,120
Someone in this city must step up.

115
00:04:25,120 --> 00:04:26,879
Tomorrow, I'll have Ren'an Hall fully cooperate.

116
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:29,600
Those who have died in their homes

117
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:30,920
will not be rescued.

118
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:32,680
But isn't that

119
00:04:33,199 --> 00:04:34,519
a bit too extreme?

120
00:04:36,360 --> 00:04:38,199
If the goal is to save lives,

121
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:41,759
the means don't have to be gentle.

122
00:04:42,279 --> 00:04:43,240
Besides,

123
00:04:44,199 --> 00:04:45,560
don't we still have the Women's clinic?

124
00:04:48,279 --> 00:04:49,639
You mean

125
00:04:50,120 --> 00:04:52,759
we play the good cop,

126
00:04:52,759 --> 00:04:53,839
and you play the bad cop?

127
00:04:55,240 --> 00:04:56,120
I believe

128
00:04:57,040 --> 00:04:58,079
you will cure them.

129
00:04:59,480 --> 00:04:59,959
Okay.

130
00:05:01,079 --> 00:05:02,199
If the caravan is allowed to enter the city,

131
00:05:02,759 --> 00:05:04,040
I'll have them send the medicine

132
00:05:04,240 --> 00:05:04,639
straight to the women's clinic.

133
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:08,439
Thank you.

134
00:05:10,360 --> 00:05:11,160
No need to thank me.

135
00:05:12,759 --> 00:05:14,040
I'm your husband.

136
00:05:16,319 --> 00:05:17,560
My husband...

137
00:05:17,759 --> 00:05:19,000
You guys talk.

138
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:20,120
I'll be on my way.

139
00:06:25,199 --> 00:06:26,160
I found it.

140
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:29,920
In the Guangji Prescriptions

141
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:31,399
issued by the Imperial Medical Dept,

142
00:06:31,639 --> 00:06:33,040
there is a prescription for malaria

143
00:06:33,199 --> 00:06:34,360
and a cold-relieving emergency powder.

144
00:06:34,639 --> 00:06:35,759
Their treatment approach

145
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:37,680
corresponds to the symptoms of the epidemic.

146
00:06:40,279 --> 00:06:41,240
Malaria.

147
00:06:59,199 --> 00:07:02,600
Malaria is caused by the hot and humid toxic air

148
00:07:03,240 --> 00:07:05,040
in the mountains and streams.

149
00:07:05,879 --> 00:07:07,000
It causes fever and chills,

150
00:07:07,759 --> 00:07:08,600
and may occur daily

151
00:07:09,040 --> 00:07:10,240
[or every other day.]

152
00:07:10,879 --> 00:07:11,759
[The toxic gases internally press,]

153
00:07:12,439 --> 00:07:14,279
[causing blood stasis and bone marrow depletion.]

154
00:07:14,959 --> 00:07:15,920
[If the malaria is not deeply rooted,]

155
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:17,319
[it can be cured with swift treatment.]

156
00:07:18,199 --> 00:07:19,680
[But if the toxins have reached the deepest parts,]

157
00:07:20,199 --> 00:07:21,360
[even with the most efficacious remedies,]

158
00:07:21,639 --> 00:07:22,439
[it's hard to save.]

159
00:07:22,920 --> 00:07:23,800
The collapse...

160
00:07:25,560 --> 00:07:26,199
No wonder.

161
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:29,600
Chang'an has been experiencing continuous rainy days.

162
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:33,639
The puddles on the streets have turned green.

163
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:36,800
Mosquitoes are three times more than in previous years.

164
00:07:38,360 --> 00:07:39,360
Anyone infected

165
00:07:40,519 --> 00:07:41,399
will experience

166
00:07:41,839 --> 00:07:42,839
alternating chills and fever within three days.

167
00:07:43,519 --> 00:07:44,040
Within seven days,

168
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:46,279
they will vomit and have bloody diarrhea.

169
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:17,800
Changshan for malaria,

170
00:08:18,120 --> 00:08:19,199
red cardamom for dampness,

171
00:08:20,079 --> 00:08:21,079
betelnut for killing parasites,

172
00:08:21,160 --> 00:08:22,360
Magnolia bark for regulating qi,

173
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:24,040
green tangerine peel clears dampness,

174
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:25,199
dried tangerine peel

175
00:08:25,759 --> 00:08:26,639
works with Magnolia to descend Qi,

176
00:08:27,480 --> 00:08:27,920
and licorice

177
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:29,040
reduces the toxicity of Dichroa.

178
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:30,879
This formula combines hot and cold,

179
00:08:31,199 --> 00:08:32,000
descends Qi, and clears dampness,

180
00:08:32,759 --> 00:08:33,399
effectively targeting

181
00:08:33,559 --> 00:08:34,919
malaria parasites.

182
00:08:35,519 --> 00:08:36,080
It's excellent.

183
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:41,679
Then,

184
00:08:43,240 --> 00:08:45,039
call it Seven Treasures Decoction?

185
00:08:45,639 --> 00:08:46,639
That's perfect.

186
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:48,360
Also,

187
00:08:49,679 --> 00:08:51,080
for those with high fever and convulsions,

188
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:52,279
prick the Ten Projections points

189
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:54,559
to release blood

190
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:55,879
and reduce heat.

191
00:08:56,679 --> 00:08:57,840
For those persistently delirious,

192
00:08:58,519 --> 00:08:59,080
prick and bleed

193
00:08:59,879 --> 00:09:00,960
to clear heat, awaken the mind,

194
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:01,879
and repel pathogens.

195
00:09:04,799 --> 00:09:05,360
Okay.

196
00:09:06,679 --> 00:09:07,720
Don't rush.

197
00:09:08,279 --> 00:09:09,519
Two pills per person.

198
00:09:10,159 --> 00:09:11,480
Take with boiled water.

199
00:09:14,320 --> 00:09:15,440
Don't drink raw water.

200
00:09:15,799 --> 00:09:16,919
Make sure to thoroughly dry your clothes.

201
00:09:17,559 --> 00:09:18,000
Here.

202
00:09:18,559 --> 00:09:19,600
Everyone gets some.

203
00:09:25,679 --> 00:09:26,679
Don't push from behind.

204
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:34,559
Follow the prescription

205
00:09:34,679 --> 00:09:35,720
and take it on time every day.

206
00:09:39,159 --> 00:09:40,240
I've gathered

207
00:09:40,240 --> 00:09:41,480
all the items on your list.

208
00:09:41,960 --> 00:09:43,360
Each ingredient for the Seven Treasures

209
00:09:43,759 --> 00:09:44,799
Elixir is in abundance.

210
00:09:49,679 --> 00:09:50,759
Thank heavens for you.

211
00:09:53,720 --> 00:09:55,480
His Majesty has approved your plan.

212
00:09:55,919 --> 00:09:57,200
Lady Yin, please proceed as you see fit.

213
00:09:57,759 --> 00:09:59,120
We'll do our utmost to assist you.

214
00:10:23,679 --> 00:10:24,559
Lady Yin,

215
00:10:24,559 --> 00:10:26,360
I've been having diarrhea for three days.

216
00:10:26,360 --> 00:10:27,679
I'm not sure if I can make it.

217
00:10:27,679 --> 00:10:28,799
Let me check your tongue coating.

218
00:10:28,799 --> 00:10:30,039
Don't worry, everyone.

219
00:10:30,039 --> 00:10:30,720
This disease can be cured.

220
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:32,200
As long as you don't drink raw water

221
00:10:32,200 --> 00:10:32,919
and disinfect frequently,

222
00:10:32,919 --> 00:10:33,919
you won't be infected.

223
00:10:34,399 --> 00:10:35,240
Everyone has it.

224
00:10:35,240 --> 00:10:36,639
Please be patient and wait in line.

225
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:39,240
It can all be prevented.

226
00:10:40,159 --> 00:10:41,080
Everyone, please line up over here.

227
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:42,120
Over here.

228
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:42,919
This way.

229
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:44,879
Don't worry.

230
00:10:47,200 --> 00:10:47,960
Please line up properly.

231
00:10:54,039 --> 00:10:54,360
Isn't this

232
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:56,399
the guild master who brought a corpse

233
00:10:56,399 --> 00:10:58,200
to cause trouble earlier?

234
00:10:58,919 --> 00:11:00,440
Didn't you claim the Women's Clinic caused deaths?

235
00:11:00,799 --> 00:11:01,320
So,

236
00:11:01,480 --> 00:11:02,399
you've been infected too,

237
00:11:02,519 --> 00:11:03,480
and you're here seeking treatment?

238
00:11:03,840 --> 00:11:04,360
Yes,

239
00:11:09,840 --> 00:11:10,120
I...

240
00:11:10,200 --> 00:11:10,879
I was wrong.

241
00:11:11,279 --> 00:11:12,679
I heard that Madam Yin

242
00:11:12,679 --> 00:11:14,000
has a medicine to treat the plague,

243
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:15,039
so I came to ask for it.

244
00:11:16,080 --> 00:11:16,720
President,

245
00:11:17,600 --> 00:11:18,559
aren't you afraid

246
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:20,279
that I might poison you?

247
00:11:21,480 --> 00:11:22,399
Madam Yin is a noble person.

248
00:11:22,919 --> 00:11:23,960
You won't hold this against me.

249
00:11:24,919 --> 00:11:26,879
I'm willing to donate all the remaining medicine in the warehouse.

250
00:11:27,240 --> 00:11:28,159
I only ask for forgiveness.

251
00:11:28,799 --> 00:11:29,840
Please, Madam Yin,

252
00:11:29,840 --> 00:11:30,799
give me the Seven Treasures Elixir

253
00:11:30,919 --> 00:11:32,159
to relieve the suffering of the epidemic.

254
00:11:34,679 --> 00:11:35,559
I'm counting on you.

255
00:11:43,279 --> 00:11:43,960
Thank you.

256
00:11:45,159 --> 00:11:47,039
Madam Yin, with your benevolent heart to heal the world,

257
00:11:47,320 --> 00:11:49,240
we have judged you with petty minds.

258
00:11:49,720 --> 00:11:51,440
We truly feel ashamed.

259
00:11:52,679 --> 00:11:53,399
From now on,

260
00:11:53,399 --> 00:11:55,480
if the Women's clinic needs any help,

261
00:11:56,000 --> 00:11:57,200
just let us know.

262
00:11:58,159 --> 00:11:59,600
No matter how difficult,

263
00:12:00,159 --> 00:12:02,039
we will do our best to assist.

264
00:12:03,360 --> 00:12:04,320
As healers,

265
00:12:04,840 --> 00:12:06,799
our duty is to save lives,

266
00:12:07,519 --> 00:12:09,080
not to seek rewards.

267
00:12:10,679 --> 00:12:11,159
Well said.

268
00:12:11,159 --> 00:12:13,480
Well said.

269
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:27,000
Actually,

270
00:12:27,720 --> 00:12:28,679
the people have

271
00:12:28,679 --> 00:12:29,559
in their hearts.

272
00:12:31,120 --> 00:12:32,000
Exactly.

273
00:12:32,720 --> 00:12:33,039
Duty.

274
00:12:33,440 --> 00:12:34,279
You're right.

275
00:12:38,559 --> 00:12:39,240
This plague

276
00:12:39,399 --> 00:12:40,440
is not ordinary malaria.

277
00:12:41,200 --> 00:12:43,000
It's a mix of miasma and cold moisture.

278
00:12:43,480 --> 00:12:44,360
It must be treated quickly.

279
00:12:45,240 --> 00:12:46,879
The Women's clinic has already drafted a plan.

280
00:12:47,159 --> 00:12:48,000
It's been proven effective.

281
00:12:48,399 --> 00:12:49,879
I hope you can contact the capital office

282
00:12:50,200 --> 00:12:50,960
to post notices

283
00:12:51,919 --> 00:12:52,879
to inform the public

284
00:12:53,200 --> 00:12:54,080
of preventive measures.

285
00:12:58,480 --> 00:12:58,919
Epidemic

286
00:12:59,320 --> 00:13:00,240
arises from impure air.

287
00:13:01,120 --> 00:13:02,159
To control it, we must address the source.

288
00:13:03,039 --> 00:13:04,200
Purify the well water

289
00:13:04,799 --> 00:13:05,960
to cut off the source of the epidemic.

290
00:13:06,480 --> 00:13:07,279
Adding alum

291
00:13:07,679 --> 00:13:08,120
and sulfur

292
00:13:08,440 --> 00:13:09,440
can disinfect the water.

293
00:13:10,360 --> 00:13:11,600
Sweep the streets daily.

294
00:13:12,440 --> 00:13:13,240
Burn realgar,

295
00:13:13,480 --> 00:13:13,879
soap pods,

296
00:13:14,240 --> 00:13:14,840
to remove impurities.

297
00:13:26,480 --> 00:13:27,159
Bodies must be covered in lime

298
00:13:27,399 --> 00:13:29,320
and burned to prevent the spread

299
00:13:30,039 --> 00:13:31,240
of the disease.

300
00:14:08,559 --> 00:14:09,759
Lady Yin!

301
00:14:10,440 --> 00:14:11,679
Lady Yin!
